o automatic versioning logic** — static file only\n\n**Design note:** From design doc (2026-03-06), version is a \"project version counter\" intended for tracking project schema versions. Currently just contains \"1\" as initial value.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Absolute File Paths\n\n1. `/workspace/cmd/cloche/init.go` — Main init command implementation\n2. `/workspace/cmd/cloche/init_test.go` — Comprehensive init tests\n3. `/workspace/internal/config/config.go` — Config package with Load functions\n4. `/workspace/internal/config/config_test.go` — Config package tests\n5. `/workspace/internal/evolution/orchestrator.go` — Evolution pipeline orchestrator\n6. `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go` — Web API handlers including handleAPIProjectInfo\n7. `/workspace/.cloche/version` — Project version file (content: \"1\")\n8. `/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md` — Latest init design document\n9. `/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-23-cloche-init-design.md` — Earlier init design reference"}],"totalDurationMs":41091,"totalTokens":60546,"totalToolUseCount":23,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":330,"cache_read_input_tokens":58473,"output_tokens":1739,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":330},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
